DefGroove BigBandIntro  4 bar introduction.

////////////

Groove BigBand

Walk Sequence	W1234   /  W13   {1 8 90; 1.5 2 100}  

Begin Chord
	Sequence   *   *   *   C1
End


Begin Chord-Hits1
	Sequence  {1 8. 95; 2.75 4. 90}  /  /  {1 2. 80}
	Voice AltoSax
	Voicing Mode=Optimal
	Volume f
    Articulate 80
    Octave 5
	Rskip 10
End

DefGroove BigBandIntro2  Alternate 4 bar introduction.

/// 8 bars

Groove BigBand

Seqsize 8

Walk Sequence	z  W1234 z W1234 z W1234 z z

Begin Bass
    Define S1 1 4 1 90; 2 4 1 90; 3 4 3 90; 4 4 5 90
	Voice $_Walk_Voice
	Octave $_Walk_Octave
	Articulate 90
	Volume f
	Rvolume 4
	Sequence S1  z S1 z S1 z S1 B13
End

Begin Chord
	Define S1  1 4. 90; 2.75 8. 90
    Define S2  1.75 8. 90; 3 8. 9
	Sequence S1 S2 S1 S2 S1 S2 C13 C1
	Voice Trombone
	Voicing  Mode=Optimal Rmove=0
	Articulate 80
	Octave 5
	Volume mf
	Rvolume 9
End

Begin Chord-Hits1
	Sequence	{ 1 4 90 0 90 0; 4 8 90 0 90 0 } { 2 8 90 0 90 0; 3 4 90 0 90 0 }
	Voice Trumpet
	Voicing Mode=Optimal
	Articulate 90
	Volume ff
	Octave 5
	Rvolume 5
	Rskip 0
End


DefGroove BigBandIntro8  8 bar introduction.

